gobblin.dataset

Interface IterableDatasetFinder<T extends Dataset>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DatasetsFinder<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IterableDatasetFinderImpl

    public interface IterableDatasetFinder<T extends Dataset>
extends DatasetsFinder<T>
    A DatasetsFinder that can return the Datasets as an Iterator. This allows Datasets to be created on demand instead of all at once, possibly reducing memory usage and improving performance.
